translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あら、気配を感じると思ったらあなた！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh, I thought I felt someone's presence—it was you!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そんなところにいたのね！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You were in a place like that!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「最近よく会うわね。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "We’ve been meeting a lot recently.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私に会いに来るくらいなら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you’re coming to see me,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 別の子に会った方がいいわよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you’d be better off meeting someone else."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「って、そーんなことどうでもいいわ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But, ah, that kind of thing doesn’t matter!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 聞いて聞いて、聞いてよあなた！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Listen, listen, listen to me, you!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さっきね、中庭で焚き火で
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Just now, in the courtyard, by the bonfire,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 焼き芋作っていた人達がいたの！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: there were people making roasted sweet potatoes!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「焼き芋イベント来たーって思いながら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I thought, 'The roasted sweet potato event is here!'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私、ワクワクしながら見守っていたんだけど！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I was watching excitedly!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 予想通り人が集まってきてテンション爆上げ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As expected, people gathered and the mood skyrocketed!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ランス様が美味しそうにお芋食べていて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Lord Rance was eating the sweet potato deliciously,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルちゃんさんに小っちゃい芋だけあげるけど、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: he only gave a small potato to Seale-chan,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それでも普通に喜ばれちゃったから取り上げて！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and even so, she was happily pleased, so he took it back!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なのに、それをリセットちゃん様に叱られて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But then, Reset-chan scolded him,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 渋々ちゃんとした芋をあげるんだけど、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and reluctantly he gave a proper potato,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 結局皆で仲良く芋食べる時点でぐはーっだけど！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but when everyone was eating potatoes together, it was just... gah!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だったんだけど！　まだ続きがあって！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That was it, but! There’s more to the story!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うはーーーっ、ごめんちょっと落ち着かせて！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Uwaaa—sorry, let me calm down a bit!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はあ、はあ……ごめんね……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Haa, haa... sorry..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: よし……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Alright..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「でね、でね、でね！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "So, so, so!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お芋大好きまそーさんも一緒に食べてたんだけど、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Masou-san, who loves sweet potatoes, was eating with us,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ジュリアちゃん先輩がほっぺの芋取ってあげたの！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Julia-senpai took the sweet potato off his cheek for him!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まそーさんも照れ臭そうに笑っていてね！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Masou-san was smiling shyly, you see!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「まずまそーさんがほっぺに芋つけてる時点で、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "First off, Masou-san having a potato stuck on his cheek is just,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うぎゃぎゃーなんだけど、ほら、これってアレ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ugyagya— but you know, this is that!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: イラーピュの時にみんなで芋食べたときの奴！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It’s from when we all ate sweet potatoes during the Ilapyu event!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「私ね、あそこでジュリアちゃん先輩の
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You know, I really loved seeing Masou-san take the roasted sweet potato off Julia-senpai’s cheek there!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 頬についてる焼き芋を取ってあげるまそーさんが
やっべぇぇぇくらい好きだったんだけどね！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It was seriously awesome!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それを！　今！　また！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "And now! Again!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 逆の立場でとかオイオイははーん
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the opposite role? Oh ho ho—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これさては世界で私だけ狙い撃ちだなぁ！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This must mean I’m the only one targeted in the whole world, right!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「って具合で、もうきゃーって感じなのよーー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Like that, it’s just like, kyaaa— that’s how I feel!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヌヌハラはその場で足をジタバタさせていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nunuhara was kicking her feet on the spot.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あーもう！　あなたに会えて良かった！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, jeez! I’m glad I met you!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんなの一人で抱えてたら私もう、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If I had kept all this to myself,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんかもう、とんでもない、もう！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I’d be just utterly overwhelmed, seriously!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「もうううううう！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Mooooooreeee!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あっ！　なんかもう、二周回って泣けてきた！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah! Now I’m going around twice and starting to cry!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はあ……はあ……はあ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Haa... haa... haa..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、ごめんね……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, sorry..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 少し落ち着いてきた……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I’m starting to calm down a little..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ところで、今更なんだけど……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "By the way, it’s kind of late to ask, but..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「私ってなんであなたと会話できるの？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Why am I able to have a conversation with you?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、うん、確かに今更なんだけどね、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, yeah, it is kind of late to ask,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ほら、私って基本的にこの世界のことしか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you know, I basically only know about this world..."
